1.2.2.name: wordpress/cimy-swift-smtp
1.2.2.description: This plug-in is for all people that have an hosting server with the php default mail function disabled and/or want to use their own SMTP servers. Supports SSL/TLS/STARTTLS encryption methods. Uses Swift Mailer engine - http://swiftmailer.org/
